00:13:14.968 --> 00:13:16.527
ver ken dos gleybn?

00:13:16.527 --> 00:13:18.283
keyner ken dos nit gleybn.

00:13:18.722 --> 00:13:20.808
geshlofn tsvishn toyte.

00:13:21.017 --> 00:13:22.614
ken men dos gleybn?

00:13:23.245 --> 00:13:25.791
tsvey vokhn tsayt opgeven ⟨a,⟩

00:13:25.791 --> 00:13:29.044
vu, gegesn malines, un nit getrunken.

00:13:29.826 --> 00:13:32.244
ken men gleybn? me gleybt dos nit.

00:13:37.686 --> 00:13:43.267
 der lebn iz geven aza; m'iz shoyn geven azoy ayngeveynt far di daytshn.

00:13:43.267 --> 00:13:46.428
s'iz geven tsaytn vos kh'hob zikh bahaltn bay di daytshn gufe,

00:13:46.428 --> 00:13:47.731
oyf di beydemer,

00:13:47.731 --> 00:13:49.701
un opgelegn gantse nekht,

00:13:49.701 --> 00:13:50.998
zikh nit bavegt.

00:13:52.793 --> 00:13:54.187
 kh'hob oysgehaltn.

00:13:54.936 --> 00:13:57.360
un in lebn darf men hobn mazl.

00:14:02.192 --> 00:14:08.396
ayere mitarbeter oyf der arbet, vi flegn, zey flegn visn dos tsu nit?

00:14:09.752 --> 00:14:13.496
zey hobn gevust, ober litvishe hobn nit gegleybt.

00:14:13.496 --> 00:14:16.040
nit gegleybt. yidn flegn gleybn.

00:14:16.148 --> 00:14:18.268
nu, a teyl zaynen geven fun di,

00:14:18.780 --> 00:14:22.385
fun di, fun di yidn vos zaynen geven in di lagern.

00:14:22.611 --> 00:14:26.638
a teyl zaynen geven vos m'hot bafrayt fun di zekhtsete divizye.

00:14:26.965 --> 00:14:30.891
di hobn gegleybt, vayl zey zaynen durkhgegangen di shtetlekh un di derfer.

00:14:32.061 --> 00:14:35.622
zey hobn gezen vos s'tut zikh in di shtetlekh un vos s'tut zikh in di derfer.

00:14:36.786 --> 00:14:38.637
ikh bin geven in Keydaner,

00:14:38.637 --> 00:14:39.767
mit di froy.

00:14:40.161 --> 00:14:43.834
zogt a ⟨L- ts- ⟩, zi hot dortn geha- dray hayzer.

00:14:44.008 --> 00:14:47.107
far yeder tokhter a shtub, der tate hot gekoyft.

00:14:47.248 --> 00:14:49.284
der tate hot gehandlt mit tvue.

00:14:49.290 --> 00:14:50.898
punkt lebn koshtshol,

00:14:50.898 --> 00:14:51.883
in Shat.

00:14:52.142 --> 00:14:54.583
dos iz ayer froy's?

00:14:53.543 --> 00:14:55.328
neyn, ye, mayn froy.

00:14:55.328 --> 00:14:57.014
lebt a litvinke.

00:14:57.014 --> 00:15:00.432
zogt zi, zi hot gekoyft bay eynem a ⟨JURGIS⟩ dortn, a familye.

00:15:00.432 --> 00:15:02.447
zog ikh, "vu lebt der ⟨JURGIS⟩?"

00:15:02.537 --> 00:15:04.286
zogt zi, "er iz shoyn geshtorbn."

00:15:05.001 --> 00:15:07.526
"nu," zog ikh, "gut. er iz geshtorbn, geshtorbn."

00:15:08.730 --> 00:15:10.141
zog ikh tsu ir,

00:15:10.300 --> 00:15:13.264
"du veyst, ⟨ah, a-⟩ az di shtub iz mayne?"

00:15:13.928 --> 00:15:15.272
zogt zi...

00:15:15.632 --> 00:15:17.111
ikh zog oyf litvish...

00:15:17.252 --> 00:15:21.060
zogt zi, "UNK."

00:15:21.825 --> 00:15:24.941
un zog ikh tsu ir azoy: "ober di shtub iz mayne."

00:15:27.310 --> 00:15:28.569
"UNK."

00:15:29.790 --> 00:15:34.247
az ikh bin arayn in, i- in Lite, in di MINISTERSTVe,

00:15:34.247 --> 00:15:37.412
zogt men mir azoy: "PRI- kum tsu forn oyf karik,

00:15:38.093 --> 00:15:40.956
nem di litvishe GR-, birgershaft.

00:15:40.995 --> 00:15:43.301
in a yor arum vestu kenen farkoyfn."

00:15:45.535 --> 00:15:48.448
ikh hob zey gevizn mayn ershtn pas, dem litvishn.

00:15:51.061 --> 00:15:52.383
ot azoy iz geblibn.

00:15:52.383 --> 00:15:55.051
tsu kumen do oyf birgershaft,

00:15:55.051 --> 00:15:57.206
un dernokh farkoyfn far zeks toyznt

00:15:57.347 --> 00:15:59.247
dolar, tsu far finf toyznt,

00:15:59.247 --> 00:16:00.443
tsu far fir toyznt,

00:16:00.443 --> 00:16:02.589
vet der advokat nemen merer gelt.

00:16:05.987 --> 00:16:10.723
dos vos ir hot ibergelebt hot gehat a virkung oyf velkhe nit iz ayere,

00:16:10.847 --> 00:16:12.663
 nu, trit in lebn?

00:16:12.838 --> 00:16:14.283
nor nervn.

00:16:14.475 --> 00:16:16.927
nor nervn, merer keyn zakh nit.

00:16:17.277 --> 00:16:21.484
di ershte tsayt fleg ikh in mitn der nakht derlangen a sh⟨up⟩, a shprung.

00:16:21.484 --> 00:16:23.197
fleg dukhtn az me shist,

00:16:23.197 --> 00:16:24.326
me yogt,

00:16:24.326 --> 00:16:25.741
fleg ikh gebn a shprung.

00:16:26.710 --> 00:16:29.432
⟨,⟩ vayl di froy iz dokh oykh geven in di lagern.

00:16:29.432 --> 00:16:31.999
f⟨leg zi zogn,⟩ "vos hot pasirt?" zog ikh, "keyn zakh nit."

00:16:32.211 --> 00:16:34.408
flegt mir oyskumen in gantsn vi ⟨s'-⟩...

00:16:34.408 --> 00:16:36.312
ikh fleg shrayen in mitn der nakht,

00:16:36.548 --> 00:16:37.841
di ershte tsayt,

00:16:38.488 --> 00:16:39.882
ober dernokh...

