00:16:54.013 --> 00:16:55.870
iber der gantser velt dos.

00:16:55.870 --> 00:16:57.213
dos iz vos ikh vil nor,

00:16:57.928 --> 00:16:59.542
az me zol lebn fray,

00:17:01.033 --> 00:17:02.512
